acme.name: Versailles Dining Table
acme.description: KD, Round Pedestal Table (Oversized Scrolled Legs/No Storage) Wooden Fixed Top & Apron Single Pedestal Base: Oversized Scrolled Legs and Crossbar Support (Poly Resin with Antique Contrast Finish)
acme.short_description: Irresistibly inviting, the Versailles collection displays the unrivaled beauty of the traditional dining. The table reflects highly decorative base with oversized scrolled feet, upholstered and tapestried chairs with the Nailhead trim accents, presenting a classic character and luxurious detailing dining room for you.
